imdb.plot outline: The JERSEY series tells the story of Malcolm Graves, played by Alonzo Herran Jr., who is the mayor of Newark, NJ. Mayor Graves is trying to recover from an assassination attempt as his personal life starts spiraling out of control. His son, Elijah Graves wants to test his manhood by following the wrong crowd, however, Elijah's new friends have a hidden agenda. At the same time his brother Drew Graves who was working as his aide, plans on starting an illegal street empire, that ends in a bloody mess with the mob. His wife Miasha Graves wants out of their loveless marriage and tries to distance herself, but can she? Stuck between a rock and a hard place, Malcolm is forced to get his hands dirty on the dark side of the streets again. Will he survive this go-around? Or will he be the cause his son's demise as well as his own?
imdb.title: Jersey: The Series
plot: Surviving an assassination attempt, a gritty Newark Mayor fights to regain control of his life and city while saving his son from the mistakes he's made in the past. Based on the feature films; Living With No Regrets, and King of Newark.
